{"tid":1596732,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住 其實我內心都只係一個毒撚","createTime":"2019-09-26T15:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T22:35:50.000Z","uid":307195,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7a9c1ba4da8f9cf7b9f7a98a875c1d324e5f5c","tid":1596732,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:31:08.000Z","msg":"其實我份人好假㗎 <br />\n<br />\n其實我真係可以好虛偽㗎<br />\n<br />\n我內心已經封閉咗十幾年<br />\n<br />\n我真係好難同人講自己最內心既諗法<br />\n<br />\n有時候我連自己都搞唔清楚自己吖你明唔明啊？<br />\n<br />\n我真係好攰<br />\n<br />\n我真係好多野煩<br />\n<br />\n我真係好多野要顧忌<br />\n<br />\n我呢世都將會係咁<br />\n<br />\n唔好再理我啦好冇<br />\n<br />\n由得我啦好嗎"},{"pid":"14a197a430c9bd2d2cba566414abf0a3ce86e14d","tid":1596732,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n逃避下 比自己靜下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265bf3e0223a3fecec6519ec7424f6488dd6e989","tid":1596732,"uid":168551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:13:26.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<br />\n真係唔識點表達出黎<br />\n有人問我點解唔開心我都唔識點答<br />\n因為我自己都唔知點解"},{"pid":"369532c279b24694d4e89e762a570a908be21186","tid":1596732,"uid":288093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15444439c98a9e6f0803ed25a3ffe2cca5d299a6","tid":1596732,"uid":296465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:22:14.000Z","msg":"唔得 俾我了解 你講既 我都會想知"},{"pid":"517f70358074c34f5c2536f1fffa1a391c961693","tid":1596732,"uid":201598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"無論咩事<br />\n我都會支持你"},{"pid":"bdc49bbca74ae910d5edc649d2e6c974aba2b7b4","tid":1596732,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:52:38.000Z","msg":"其實都幾有趣<br />\n自己都搞唔明自己，<br />\n即係個人有好多諗法，有思想嘅人<br />\n嘗試慢慢了解自己，慢慢俾人了解你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都努力緊"},{"pid":"4536c209c835c77373967ad19bf8daaeb3539c23","tid":1596732,"uid":43685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T18:47:20.000Z","msg":"又有唔想講既野，又有啲嘢唔會有人拎黎講，結果就係好多野諗但係又冇嘢講<br />\n我唔會話叫你試下揾人講同人講，因為連我自己都做唔到，不過可以試下想像自己裏面有另一個自己，由自己去聆聽自己既想法，由一個抽離少少既自己去嘗試了解自己，我暫時都係靠咁樣去開解自己"},{"pid":"121243a305b7a8e2673dd409d72759eeb427f44b","tid":1596732,"uid":157735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T18:51:27.000Z","msg":"我都係 一個外在性毒L<br />\n平時好outgoing 興趣都好多<br />\n但就係好中意自己一個 自我封閉 係最舒服"},{"pid":"08e0b6f6125cc807e2e0323ef23e4c4312c58072","tid":1596732,"uid":299445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121243a305b7a8e2673dd409d72759eeb427f44b","tid":1596732,"uid":157735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T18:51:27.000Z","msg":"我都係 一個外在性毒L<br />\n平時好outgoing 興趣都好多<br />\n但就係好中意自己一個 自我封閉 係最舒服"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T21:25:33.000Z","msg":"屌以為我自己打緊咁樣"},{"pid":"9af7fc8792f1a81d08e6e2a3bb00892b9dd0907a","tid":1596732,"uid":157735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e0b6f6125cc807e2e0323ef23e4c4312c58072","tid":1596732,"uid":299445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121243a305b7a8e2673dd409d72759eeb427f44b","tid":1596732,"uid":157735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T18:51:27.000Z","msg":"我都係 一個外在性毒L<br />\n平時好outgoing 興趣都好多<br />\n但就係好中意自己一個 自我封閉 係最舒服"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T21:25:33.000Z","msg":"屌以為我自己打緊咁樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"可以認識下"},{"pid":"7a7066aa90e17ca382beea9ad397c1e4cae3041e","tid":1596732,"uid":163485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T08:32:48.000Z","msg":"毒撚無問題！<br />\n只係其中一個lifestyle option"},{"pid":"c042b3e59634d83ec84bfa5df5e2f102c2c88c39","tid":1596732,"uid":299445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9af7fc8